Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants containing it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in cases that eventually reach Completed + In Call versus those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait in variants containing Accepted + Wait - User versus variants containing only Accepted + Wait
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait in process paths leading to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait when directly succeeded by Completed + Resolved versus when succeeded by Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + Closed in variants also containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Wait to be done after Accepted + Assigned in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait in variants with multiple occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment compared to those without
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Total waiting time to the Accepted + Wait activity when the case originates in Brazil versus USA versus France
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in variants that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'
